’ђђЩУTitle: title: Nushell 0.109.1
Path: Nushell 0.109.1
Content:
Today, we're releasing version 0.109.1 of Nu. This release fixes some regressions of Nu 0.109.0, especially fixes to 
``http get``
 and 
``source``
.
—ЩZarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2025-12-02-nushell_v0_109_1.mdЩ@71914960820240a9d07c724456ae1d1f1f1425dc53a196e06a1f66f9db4ea800¶title: Nushell 0.109.1‘ЇWhere to get itЪ‘Nu 0.109.1 is available as 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/releases/tag/0.109.1] pre-built binaries
 or from 
[link: https://crates.io/crates/nu] crates.io
. If you have Rust installed you can install it using 
``cargo install nu``
.
As part of this release, we also publish a set of optional 
[link: https://www.nushell.sh/book/plugins.html] plugins
 you can install and use with Nushell.
’ђђЪОTitle: title: Nushell 0.109.1
Path: Where to get it
Content:
Nu 0.109.1 is available as 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/releases/tag/0.109.1] pre-built binaries
 or from 
[link: https://crates.io/crates/nu] crates.io
. If you have Rust installed you can install it using 
``cargo install nu``
.
As part of this release, we also publish a set of optional 
[link: https://www.nushell.sh/book/plugins.html] plugins
 you can install and use with Nushell.
